query:
SELECT 
  COUNT(*) as total,
  SUM(CASE WHEN detailedDescription IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as with_desc,
  SUM(CASE WHEN particleSize IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as with_particle,
  SUM(CASE WHEN poreSize IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as with_pore,
  SUM(CASE WHEN columnLength IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as with_length,
  SUM(CASE WHEN phRange IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as with_ph
FROM products
